OL,3,CEducation Authority boss hits out at
OL,4,Ccriticisms of public services
OL,6,FThe head of the Education Authority
OL,7,Fhas hit out at criticism of public
OL,8,Fservices and employees.
OL,10,FIn an end of year message, Richard
OL,11,FPengelly said he wanted to "push back"
OL,12,Fagainst "inaccurate narratives that
OL,13,Fportray all public services and
OL,14,Femployees as always failing".
OL,16,F"I see every day the commitment of so
OL,17,Fmany people to do their absolute best
OL,18,Ffor children, young people and
OL,19,Fschools," Mr Pengelly said.
