OL,3,CEducation Authority boss hits out at
OL,4,Ccriticisms of public services
OL,6,FHe added: "I do not seek to suggest we
OL,7,Fget things right every time ` but we
OL,8,Fcertainly do so many, many more times
OL,9,Fthan we get it wrong.
OL,11,F"To suggest otherwise is both
OL,12,Finaccurate and unfair to those
OL,13,Fcolleagues who care passionately about
OL,14,Ftheir work."
OL,16,FHe said it is "undoubtedly a very
OL,17,Fdifficult time for education and for
OL,18,Fpublic services generally", adding:
OL,19,F"Funding pressures are increasingly
OL,20,Fsevere, while demand in key areas
OL,21,Fcontinues to grow."
